117
00:10:46,820 --> 00:10:50,540
That's not it. As I remember, no.

118
00:10:50,540 --> 00:10:52,880
A friend of yours, huh?

119
00:10:52,880 --> 00:10:54,940
So, Luo Ren touched your hair.

120
00:10:54,940 --> 00:10:57,200
