123
00:11:03,500 --> 00:11:05,060
But it was indeed my friend.

124
00:11:05,060 --> 00:11:06,420
Come on.

125
00:11:06,420 --> 00:11:09,340
Don't take us as fools, okay?

126
00:11:09,340 --> 00:11:12,460
